{"type": "article", "id": 17370, "title": "polygon灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-11T06:34:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061540163v1ywZea7TCBx9mI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是来自设计师 Jan Plechac 和 Henry Wielgus 的灯饰 polygon，由捷克灯具品牌 lasvit 在布拉格设计节上展出。他们结合了 3D 建模中的网格结构，在白天，灯罩可以折射出柔和的日光，到了晚上点亮灯时，能看到半透明的网格的灯罩，有点像钻石。设计师专门调和了一种香槟色，让这盏灯有了优雅的色泽。<a href=\"http://www.janandhenry.com/work/detail/id/70\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144442SFqk2LKN6mAJgaes.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"654\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261444432jduBsvwxDa6bHRG.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1023\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.25061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144443Z6t8mDfhWEy0TlPq.jpg\" width=\"525\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144444HICl4yEboL1kQGi6.jpg\" width=\"525\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}